

{"id":3484,"date":"2023-05-09T17:03:56","date_gmt":"2023-05-09T10:03:56","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tnt.locdt.site\/staging\/?p=3484"},"modified":"2023-05-16T14:45:11","modified_gmt":"2023-05-16T07:45:11","slug":"chon-giay-tap-gym-danh-cho-nguoi-moi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/chon-giay-tap-gym-phu-hop-khi-di-tap-gym\/","title":{"rendered":"Ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y t\u1eadp gym ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><b><i>C\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y khi \u0111i t\u1eadp gym, \u0111i t\u1eadp gym ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng The New Gym t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc sau: L\u01b0u \u00fd c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n khi ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y, C\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ecdn m\u1eabu gi\u00e0y, Ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1eebng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp.<\/i><\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng cho gi\u00e0y t\u1eeb g\u1ecdn nh\u1eb9, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec7m, \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00e1m ch\u1eafc, \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i, ph\u1ea3n l\u1ef1c, ch\u1ed1ng tr\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1ee3t,\u2026. nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, <strong>c\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y<\/strong> ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p khi \u0111i t\u1eadp gym l\u00e0 g\u00ec? Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n mu\u1ed1n mua gi\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00e2n v\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft n\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn lo\u1ea1i gi\u00e0y n\u00e0o ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p?\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #00a2c4; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><br \/>\nC\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y khi \u0111i t\u1eadp gym?<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><b><br \/>\n1. L\u01b0u \u00fd khi ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y:<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>N\u1eafm r\u00f5 th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n<\/b><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n n\u1eafm r\u00f5 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ed9ng, chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i, \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00f5m b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00e8 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi v\u00f3c d\u00e1ng ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi v\u00f3c d\u00e1ng ch\u00e2n s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn g\u00e2y ra nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0 \u0111au l\u00f2ng b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n, \u0111au g\u1ed1i, c\u0103ng m\u1eaft c\u00e1 ch\u00e2n,\u2026<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>Quy t\u1eafc ng\u00f3n tay c\u00e1i khi ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y<\/b><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3512\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3512\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3512 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/quy-tac-ngon-tay-cai-khi-chon-giay-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/quy-tac-ngon-tay-cai-khi-chon-giay-1.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/quy-tac-ngon-tay-cai-khi-chon-giay-1-300x152.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/quy-tac-ngon-tay-cai-khi-chon-giay-1-1024x520.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/quy-tac-ngon-tay-cai-khi-chon-giay-1-768x390.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/quy-tac-ngon-tay-cai-khi-chon-giay-1-1536x780.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/quy-tac-ngon-tay-cai-khi-chon-giay-1-2048x1040.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3512\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Quy t\u1eafc ng\u00f3n tay c\u00e1i khi ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p khi \u00f4m tr\u1ecdn g\u00f3t ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb tu\u1ed9t khi di chuy\u1ec3n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi b\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb 0,5cm \u0111\u1ebfn 1 cm t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi k\u00edch c\u1ee1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f3n tay c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed9 gi\u00e3n n\u1ee1, tr\u00e1nh b\u1ecb ch\u1eadt trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng. H\u00e3y c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn mu b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, kh\u00f4ng l\u1ecfng l\u1ebbo hay qu\u00e1 ch\u1eadt.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n kh\u00e1c nhau. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng nghi\u00ean ch\u00e2n ra b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i, khi ch\u1ea1y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 rung v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u00edt b\u1ecb ph\u00e2n t\u00e1n v\u00e0o ph\u1ea7n g\u00f3t ch\u00e2n h\u01a1n, M\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f4i gi\u00e0y v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf l\u1edbp \u0111\u00eam gi\u1ea3m ch\u1ea5n s\u1ebd h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 l\u1ef1c ph\u1ea3n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng nghi\u00eang ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o trong khi ch\u1ea1y s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f4i gi\u00e0y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 gi\u00fap \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng, gi\u00fap s\u1eefa c\u00e1c l\u1ed7i nghi\u00eang ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb v\u1eb9o v\u00e0 l\u00e0m ch\u1eadm qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh nghi\u00eang ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>6 B\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ecdn m\u1eabu gi\u00e0y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p:<\/b><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng The New Gym th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 6 b\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u1eabu gi\u00e0y\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>\u00a0B\u01b0\u1edbc 1:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec7m m\u1eaft c\u00e1 ch\u00e2n, nh\u1eefng gi\u00e0y c\u00f3 g\u00f3t qu\u00e1 cao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m y\u1ebfu m\u1eaft c\u00e1 ch\u00e2n.<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>\u00a0B\u01b0\u1edbc 2:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Nh\u1eefng gi\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebf nh\u1ecf s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m l\u1ef1c h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n l\u1ef1c, d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0 gi\u1eef th\u0103ng b\u1eb1ng, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ma s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ec1u k\u00e9m.<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>\u00a0B\u01b0\u1edbc 3:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> U\u1ed1n cong ph\u1ea7n m\u0169i gi\u00e0y khi th\u1ea5y 1\/3 gi\u00e0y u\u1ed1n m\u1ec1m d\u1ebbo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, 2\/3 v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 c\u1ee9ng c\u00e1p, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f4i gi\u00e0y t\u1ed1t. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean nh\u1ea5n v\u00e0o ph\u1ea7n \u0111u\u00f4i gi\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1eafc c\u1ee7a gi\u00e0y.<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>\u00a0B\u01b0\u1edbc 4:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> M\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f4i gi\u00e0y cho t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng h\u01a1i ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u tho\u00e1ng, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5m n\u01b0\u1edbc, mau kh\u00f4 s\u1ebd thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n cho vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mang m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f4i gi\u00e0y sau m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb h\u1ea7m, \u1ea9m v\u00e0 b\u1ed1c m\u00f9i \u0111\u00e2u.<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>\u00a0B\u01b0\u1edbc 5:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> H\u00e3y xo\u1eafn gi\u00e0y theo 2 chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c nhau \u0111\u1ec3 quan s\u00e1t. N\u1ebfu gi\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb bi\u1ebfn d\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 m\u00f3p m\u00e9o, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f4i gi\u00e0y t\u1ed1t.<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>\u00a0B\u01b0\u1edbc 6:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng may c\u1ee7a gi\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng may \u0111\u1ec1u, n\u00e9t, nh\u1ecf d\u1ecdc l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f4i gi\u00e0y t\u1ed1t.<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><b>2. Ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1eebng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng gi\u00e0y cho nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp kh\u00e1c nhau, The New Gym xin chia s\u1ebb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho t\u1eebng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp:<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>Ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y t\u1eadp gym \u0111a n\u0103ng:\u00a0<\/b><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3524\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3524\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3524 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/giay-tap-gym-da-nang-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/giay-tap-gym-da-nang-1.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/giay-tap-gym-da-nang-1-300x152.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/giay-tap-gym-da-nang-1-1024x520.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/giay-tap-gym-da-nang-1-768x390.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/giay-tap-gym-da-nang-1-1536x780.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/giay-tap-gym-da-nang-1-2048x1040.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3524\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y t\u1eadp gym \u0111a n\u0103ng<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f4i gi\u00e0y t\u1eadp k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i t\u1eadp \u0111a n\u0103ng (cardio), t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh (strength training) th\u00ec c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ki\u1ec3u gi\u00e0y h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 kh\u00e1c. D\u00e0nh cho nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi di chuy\u1ec3n ngang, t\u0103ng v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m t\u1ed1c linh ho\u1ea1t, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f4i gi\u00e0y h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ec7m v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00e1m cao. B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f3n ch\u00e2n khi mang. <\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f4i gi\u00e0y c\u00f3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nh\u1eb9 v\u00f2m ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 m\u1eaft c\u00e1 ch\u00e2n. v\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f4i gi\u00e0y nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebf h\u01a1i m\u1ecfng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng di chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 gi\u1eef th\u0103ng b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu gi\u00e0y c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m s\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ed9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>Ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 cardio: <\/b><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3516\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3516\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3516 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/chon-giay-chay-bo-cardio.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/chon-giay-chay-bo-cardio.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/chon-giay-chay-bo-cardio-300x152.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/chon-giay-chay-bo-cardio-1024x520.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/chon-giay-chay-bo-cardio-768x390.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/chon-giay-chay-bo-cardio-1536x780.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/chon-giay-chay-bo-cardio-2048x1040.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3516\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 cardio<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi gi\u00e0y d\u00f9ng tr\u00ean m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o ki\u1ec3u ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n (l\u1ec7ch trong ho\u1eb7c l\u1ec7ch ngo\u00e0i nh\u01b0 chia s\u1ebb \u1edf tr\u00ean).<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>Ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y n\u00e2ng t\u1ea1:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0<\/span><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3518\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3518\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3518 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/chon-giay-nang-ta.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/chon-giay-nang-ta.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/chon-giay-nang-ta-300x152.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/chon-giay-nang-ta-1024x520.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/chon-giay-nang-ta-768x390.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/chon-giay-nang-ta-1536x780.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/chon-giay-nang-ta-2048x1040.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3518\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/span> <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y n\u00e2ng t\u1ea1<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Khi ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng t\u1ea1, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f4i gi\u00e0y v\u1edbi c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng ph\u1eb3ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ee1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn khi n\u00e2ng t\u1ea1. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f4i gi\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec7m m\u1ec1m, d\u00e0y ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ebf cao, kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng ph\u1eb3ng, s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp n\u00e2ng t\u1ea1 v\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ed9t s\u1ed1ng, sai l\u1ec7ch t\u01b0 th\u1ebf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><b>Ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y cho Crossfit:\u00a0<\/b><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3528 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/chon-giay-cho-cross-fit-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/chon-giay-cho-cross-fit-2.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/chon-giay-cho-cross-fit-2-300x152.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/chon-giay-cho-cross-fit-2-1024x520.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/chon-giay-cho-cross-fit-2-768x390.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/chon-giay-cho-cross-fit-2-1536x780.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/chon-giay-cho-cross-fit-2-2048x1040.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Crossfit l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 cao ng\u1eaft qu\u00e3ng, l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp th\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y, bao g\u1ed3m: squat, h\u00edt \u0111\u1ea5t, n\u00e2ng t\u1ea1\u2026 B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f4i gi\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebf ph\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp crossfit.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Tham kh\u1ea3o th\u00eam:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/cach-su-dung-cac-thiet-bi-tap-luyen-tai-the-new-gym\/\">C\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i The New Gym.<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/thenewgymvietnam\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Fanpage The New Gym<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Hotline: 1900636920.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>C\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y khi \u0111i t\u1eadp gym, \u0111i t\u1eadp gym ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng The New Gym t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc sau: L\u01b0u \u00fd c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n khi ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y, C\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ecdn m\u1eabu gi\u00e0y, Ch\u1ecdn gi\u00e0y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1eebng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp. &nbsp; C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng cho gi\u00e0y t\u1eeb g\u1ecdn [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":3530,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[9],"tags":[143,144,145],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3484"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3484"}],"version-history":[{"count":18,"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3484\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4000,"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3484\/revisions\/4000"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3530"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3484"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3484"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=3484"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}